data.title: Our Mentors
data.meta_description: Our mentors, faculty and staff are committed to helping students develop practical skills, professional values and relationships that will last a lifetime.
data.text:
Thank you to all those who served as a mentor to a St. Thomas Law student this year. Your investment in our students is an essential contribution to the future of our profession. Because of you and the 1,700 experienced legal professionals who have generously contributed their time over the years, St. Thomas Law has been ranked the #2 law school in the nation for practical training. More importantly, we are able to provide each student with a supportive professional relationship that gives them real-world experience and expert advice.

A special thank you to our 2024 Mentor Appreciation Reception sponsors, Minnesota Lawyer and Minnesota Lawyers Mutual.
